      <p>First, to screen the best classification algorithm for the promoter prediction task, we have submitted our train/test data, where 20% of the data was reserved for the test, into six different classification algorithms (Table <xref rid="tbl2" ref-type="table">2</xref>), out of which XGBoost method was selected as it returned the best accuracy, precision, recall, and F1 scores.</p>
